snippet.title: Gotham City Impostors: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
When Batman is gone, what happens? In the new game Gotham City Impostors, a new FPS, you can tear apart the streets or defend them as would be heroes/villains.

IGN's YouTube is just a taste of our content. Get more:
http://www.ign.com
